trans-unit.source: Represents the removal of a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> during dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Representa a remoção de um <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> durante a atualização dinâmica.
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used by a tracking service to determine which <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s have been removed during a dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe pode ser usada por um serviço de controle para determinar qual <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s foram removidos durante a atualização dinâmica.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: An instance of this object is generated for every <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet> that is removed (that is, that existed in the workflow before this dynamic update, but is gone afterward).
trans-unit.target: Uma instância do objeto é gerada para cada <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>que está sendo removido (ou seja, que existia no fluxo de trabalho antes da atualização dinâmica, mas não existe mais posteriormente).</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction"></xref> class by using the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction"> </xref> classe usando o <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.
O <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: removedRuleSetDefinition is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: removedRuleSetDefinitioné uma referência nula ( no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets or Sets the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.
O <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> to remove from the workflow is a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> remover do fluxo de trabalho é uma referência nula (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> removido do fluxo de trabalho.
